b: when told by any flyup then add speed 0 1 0
when told by any flydown then add speed 0 -1 0
when told by any flyforward then add speed -1 0 0
when told by any flybackward then add speed 1 0 0
when told by any flyleft then add speed 0 0 1
when told by any flyright then add speed 0 0 -1
when told by any flydestroy then destroy all parts
when starts then set snap angles to 0
when told by any flystop then set speed 0
